      <h3>Creating a Stream (From URL)</h3>
      <p>To Create a Stream...</p>
      <code> http://localhost:5000/streams/create/[NAME]?[FIELD1]=&[FIELD2]=&[FIELDN]= </code>

      <h3>View a list of Streams</h3>
      <p>To view a list of all streams...</p>
      <code>http://localhost:5000/streams/view </code>

      <h3>View an Individual Stream</h3>
      <p>To view an individual stream...</p>
      <code>http://localhost:5000/streams/view/[NAME]</code>
      <p> NAME = Name of Stream </p>

      <h3>Add Data to a Stream </h3>
      <p>To add data to a Stream...</p>
      <code> http://localhost:5000/streams/input/[NAME]/[SECRET KEY]?[FIELD1]=[VAL]&[FIELD2]=[VAL]&[FIELDN]=[VAL] </code>
      <p>NAME = Name of Stream </p>
      <p>SECRET KEY = Secret key for stream</p>
      <p>FIELDN = Field names for the stream</p>
      <p> VAL = Reporting value for that field </p>

      <h3>Dowload a Stream</h3>
      <p>To download a string... </p>
      <code>http://localhost:5000/streams/download/[NAME]?format=[FORMAT]</code>
      <p>NAME = Name of Stream </p>
      <p>FORMAT = `csv` or `json`</p>

      <h3>Clear a Stream</h3>
      <p>To reset a string use... </p>
      <code>http://localhost:5000/streams/clear/[NAME]/[KEY]?backup=[BACKUP]?format=[FORMAT]</code>
      <p>NAME = Name of Stream </p>
      <p>KEY = Private key for Stream </p>
      <p>BACKUP = true or false option for downloading log before clearning</p>
      <p>FORMAT = `csv` or `json`</p>

      <h3>Delete a Stream</h3>
      <p>To delete a string... </p>
      <code>http://localhost:5000/streams/delete/[NAME]/[DELETE KEY]</code>
      <p> NAME = Name of Stream </p>
      <p> DELETE KEY = Delete key for the string </p>

